title: I tried making a living painting your weird Warhammer - and lost money
description:
Download Warhammer 40.000: Tacticus for free and enjoy a tactical Warhammer game wherever you are: https://play.tacticusgame.com/squidmar

This week, we opened up a commission painting service and tried painting what ever requests you guys had. To see if it was possible to make a living from painting Warhammer as a Commission service on Fiverr.

🖌️🧟‍♂️👕 Support us by buying the exclusive Squidmar Brushes, Merchandice & sona miniatures: https://www.squidmar.com/shop
